{"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Alias","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Lean.Elab.Command","Lean.Elab.Term","Lean"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L141-L158","name":"Tactic.Alias.elabAliasLRDots","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.elabAliasLRDots","doc":"Elaborates an `alias ↔ ..` command. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L128-L138","name":"Tactic.Alias.elabAliasLR","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.elabAliasLR","doc":"Elaborates an `alias ↔` command. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L115-L125","name":"Tactic.Alias.aliasIff","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.aliasIff","doc":"Given a constant representing an iff decl, adds a decl for one of the implication\ndirections.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L104-L109","name":"Tactic.Alias.mkIffMpApp","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.mkIffMpApp","doc":"Given a possibly forall-quantified iff expression `prf`, produce a value for one\nof the implication directions (determined by `mp`).\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L77-L98","name":"Tactic.Alias.elabAlias","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.elabAlias","doc":"Elaborates an `alias ←` command. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L70-L74","name":"Tactic.Alias.appendNamespace","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.appendNamespace","doc":"Like `++`, except that if the right argument starts with `_root_` the namespace will be\nignored.\n```\nappendNamespace `a.b `c.d = `a.b.c.d\nappendNamespace `a.b `_root_.c.d = `c.d\n```\n\nTODO: Move this declaration to a more central location.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L58-L59","name":"Tactic.Alias.aliasLRDots","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.aliasLRDots","doc":"Adds one-way implication declarations, inferring names for them. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L55-L56","name":"Tactic.Alias.aliasLR","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.aliasLR","doc":"Adds one-way implication declarations. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.lean#L52-L53","name":"Tactic.Alias.alias","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Alias.html#Tactic.Alias.alias","doc":"Adds some copies of a theorem or definition. "}]}